            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "LiDAR acquisition, processing and QC for 12 western NC counties / Imagery acquisition, process and QC for 13 western NC counties.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Progressive delivery to the Collaboratory and NCEM of data up through May 2025.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Aircraft are mobilizing with expected acquisition for lidar to begin by weekend of 1/11-1/12, weather dependent",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Acquisition for lidar running in tandem with NCEM project – teams will collect lines each day based on weather windows",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Lidar acquisition could likely take 4-5 weeks depending on weather",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Orthophotography data capture to begin in late January once appropriate sun angle is achieved",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Lidar to be processed in blocks and delivered intermittently when data is ready",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Orthophotography will be rectified against new lidar DEM data, except in Alexander that will use the existing DEM for rectification with updates only in areas of change",
